1
00:01:16,319 --> 00:01:17,319
Tian'er

2
00:01:17,640 --> 00:01:18,959
I'm back.

3
00:02:02,200 --> 00:02:03,560
You seem to be in good spirits today.

4
00:02:05,159 --> 00:02:07,359
Good news lifts the spirits.

5
00:02:07,359 --> 00:02:08,759
You're getting cheeky again.

6
00:02:14,879 --> 00:02:16,560
Looks pretty good.

7
00:02:18,479 --> 00:02:19,240
Let me have a taste.

8
00:02:21,120 --> 00:02:22,400
This isn't for you.

9
00:02:22,800 --> 00:02:23,719
Make your own if you want some.

10
00:02:24,560 --> 00:02:25,520
Stingy.

11
00:02:25,599 --> 00:02:27,240
Master went out early this morning.

12
00:02:27,240 --> 00:02:28,000
Besides...

13
00:02:28,080 --> 00:02:29,639
You can eat two bowls by yourself.

14
00:02:34,240 --> 00:02:35,280
My Mom is back.

15
00:02:35,800 --> 00:02:36,840
This is for her.

16
00:02:46,759 --> 00:02:47,280
Mom.

17
00:02:52,879 --> 00:02:54,680
Didn't his mom die long ago?

18
00:02:56,960 --> 00:02:57,479
Mom.

19
00:02:57,840 --> 00:02:58,879
Come taste my cooking.

20
00:03:03,120 --> 00:03:03,960
Do you remember?

21
00:03:04,439 --> 00:03:05,159
Since I was little...

22
00:03:05,520 --> 00:03:07,680
you loved making me Noodles with Tomato and Egg Sauce.

23
00:03:08,599 --> 00:03:09,479
You have no idea...

24
00:03:09,879 --> 00:03:11,840
not seeing you for so many years...

25
00:03:11,960 --> 00:03:13,240
I've learned to make it myself.

26
00:03:13,840 --> 00:03:14,240
Here.

27
00:03:24,120 --> 00:03:24,680
Mom.

28
00:03:25,520 --> 00:03:26,240
Have a taste.

29
00:03:44,680 --> 00:03:45,199
Mom.

30
00:03:45,479 --> 00:03:46,280
How does it taste?

31
00:04:04,520 --> 00:04:05,080
Mom.

32
00:04:05,520 --> 00:04:06,520
I've been an unfilial son.

33
00:04:07,759 --> 00:04:08,800
Master.

34
00:04:10,879 --> 00:04:11,400
Mmh.

35
00:04:12,400 --> 00:04:12,879
Mom.

36
00:04:13,719 --> 00:04:15,360
I never had the chance to be with you before.

37
00:04:15,840 --> 00:04:17,720
I'll stay by your side and take care of you every day.

38
00:04:18,000 --> 00:04:18,639
Okay?

39
00:04:30,480 --> 00:04:30,920
Mom

40
00:04:31,480 --> 00:04:32,439
You should get some rest now.

41
00:04:32,839 --> 00:04:33,800
I'll come see you again tomorrow.

42
00:04:41,439 --> 00:04:42,079
Uncle

43
00:04:46,879 --> 00:04:47,519
Uncle

44
00:04:47,639 --> 00:04:48,399
Mom is tired.

45
00:04:48,519 --> 00:04:49,199
If there's anything,

46
00:04:49,279 --> 00:04:50,120
talk to her tomorrow.

47
00:04:53,519 --> 00:04:54,560
Master

48
00:04:54,560 --> 00:04:56,199
Is he seeing a ghost?

49
00:04:59,839 --> 00:05:02,959
What must come will come.

50
00:05:06,079 --> 00:05:06,680
Mom

51
00:05:07,279 --> 00:05:08,480
With your bad back,

52
00:05:08,839 --> 00:05:10,560
you need a soft mattress like this

53
00:05:11,439 --> 00:05:12,720
to ease the strain on your body.

54
00:05:13,800 --> 00:05:14,920
That should fix it.

55
00:05:16,240 --> 00:05:16,879
Mom

56
00:05:16,879 --> 00:05:17,360
Come.

57
00:05:18,160 --> 00:05:19,040
Come try it out.

58
00:05:19,800 --> 00:05:20,480
Careful.

59
00:05:23,240 --> 00:05:23,839
How is it?

60
00:05:28,720 --> 00:05:29,120
Mom

61
00:05:29,439 --> 00:05:30,199
I'll get the door.

62
00:05:38,639 --> 00:05:39,560
What are you doing here?

63
00:05:39,920 --> 00:05:41,959
Why are you still up this late?

64
00:05:43,480 --> 00:05:44,759
Mom's back is bothering her.

65
00:05:44,839 --> 00:05:45,959
I'm changing her bedding.

66
00:05:49,480 --> 00:05:51,519
What's this?

67
00:05:52,839 --> 00:05:55,600
I made Auntie some Lotus Seed Porridge.

68
00:05:55,680 --> 00:05:56,800
Let me take it in to her.

69
00:05:58,000 --> 00:05:59,160
I didn't know you had such skills.

70
00:05:59,279 --> 00:05:59,720
Come.

71
00:05:59,839 --> 00:06:00,519
Come on in.

72
00:06:02,639 --> 00:06:03,319
Mom

73
00:06:03,439 --> 00:06:04,920
Bailing made you some Lotus Seed Porridge.

74
00:06:14,720 --> 00:06:15,160
Here.

75
00:06:15,319 --> 00:06:15,879
Give it to me.

76
00:06:22,079 --> 00:06:23,040
It smells pretty good.

77
00:06:23,439 --> 00:06:23,879
Mom

78
00:06:24,399 --> 00:06:25,079
Let me feed you.

79
00:06:30,839 --> 00:06:31,639
Eat slowly.

80
00:06:37,279 --> 00:06:37,639
Here.

81
00:06:42,560 --> 00:06:43,639
Wake up!

82
00:06:45,800 --> 00:06:46,920
Haven't you gone crazy enough?

83
00:06:49,959 --> 00:06:51,480
Your mom died long ago.

84
00:06:55,959 --> 00:06:56,560
Mom

85
00:06:56,839 --> 00:06:57,480
It's okay.

86
00:06:57,800 --> 00:06:58,759
She's talking nonsense.

87
00:07:00,399 --> 00:07:02,120
Didn't you tell me to be strong?

88
00:07:02,720 --> 00:07:04,639
Didn't you tell me every day to be brave?

89
00:07:05,000 --> 00:07:06,439
What are you doing?

90
00:07:08,160 --> 00:07:09,439
You're disturbing Mom.

91
00:07:10,319 --> 00:07:11,360
Please get out.

92
00:07:12,800 --> 00:07:14,639
Stop fooling yourself, okay?

93
00:07:15,399 --> 00:07:16,879
Your mom died long ago.

94
00:07:17,199 --> 00:07:18,720
You know it in your heart.

95
00:07:22,639 --> 00:07:23,639
The way you are now...

96
00:07:24,000 --> 00:07:25,560
how is it different from a coward?

97
00:07:35,519 --> 00:07:36,600
Mom needs to rest.

98
00:07:37,879 --> 00:07:39,360
Please don't disturb her.

99
00:07:42,199 --> 00:07:43,160
Your mom...

100
00:07:43,639 --> 00:07:44,439
Your mom...

101
00:07:44,439 --> 00:07:45,480
Where is your mom?

102
00:07:45,480 --> 00:07:46,800
Where is she?

103
00:07:46,800 --> 00:07:47,800
Tell her to come out!

104
00:07:47,800 --> 00:07:48,560
That's enough!

105
00:07:52,000 --> 00:07:52,560
Mom

106
00:07:54,079 --> 00:07:54,920
Are you okay?

107
00:07:55,079 --> 00:07:55,839
Bailing is still young.

108
00:07:55,839 --> 00:07:56,439
She doesn't know better.

109
00:07:56,639 --> 00:07:57,720
Don't hold it against her.

110
00:07:58,480 --> 00:08:00,279
I'll remake the bed for you in a bit, okay?

111
00:08:02,600 --> 00:08:03,560
Don't be angry.

112
00:08:05,519 --> 00:08:06,040
Mom

113
00:08:07,199 --> 00:08:08,439
Rest well for a while.

114
00:08:10,279 --> 00:08:11,199
It's okay, Mom.

115
00:08:34,559 --> 00:08:35,480
In all these years,

116
00:08:35,840 --> 00:08:38,000
this is the first time Master has seen you cry.

117
00:08:38,840 --> 00:08:39,919
Master

118
00:08:39,919 --> 00:08:41,440
Please help him, okay?

119
00:08:42,080 --> 00:08:43,919
I don't want to see him like this.

120
00:08:51,200 --> 00:08:52,399
It seems

121
00:08:52,399 --> 00:08:54,159
you've really grown up.

122
00:09:04,080 --> 00:09:05,159
Tian'er

123
00:09:05,720 --> 00:09:07,320
is a good child.

124
00:09:26,879 --> 00:09:27,600
Tian'er

125
00:09:27,879 --> 00:09:29,639
Mom has to go out for a bit.

126
00:09:29,840 --> 00:09:30,720
I'll be back soon

127
00:09:30,799 --> 00:09:32,240
to make you Noodles with Tomato and Egg Sauce.

128
00:09:32,799 --> 00:09:33,440
Okay?

129
00:09:34,000 --> 00:09:35,159
I know, Mom.

130
00:09:43,399 --> 00:09:44,080
Mom

131
00:10:04,879 --> 00:10:05,480
Mom

132
00:10:15,320 --> 00:10:15,960
Mom

133
00:10:26,519 --> 00:10:27,120
Mom

134
00:10:46,960 --> 00:10:47,639
Where's Mom?

135
00:10:48,399 --> 00:10:49,159
Where is Mom?

136
00:10:50,759 --> 00:10:51,799
Mom went out.
